(V) Rules for use of your personal information
1. We will use the personal information collected in accordance with the terms of this Privacy Policy and for the purpose of implementing our products and/or services.
2. After collecting your personal information, we will use technical means to de-identify the data. The de-identified information will not identify the subject. Please understand and agree that in this case we have the right to use the information that has been de-identified; And without disclosing your personal information, we have the right to analyze and commercialize the user database.
3. Please note that all personal information you provide when using our products and/or services will continue to be licensed to us for the duration of your use of our products and/or services unless you delete or refuse to collect it through your system settings. When you cancel your account, we will stop using and delete your personal information.
